snippet.title: "Ultra Firepower, Infinity Enemies" - Outpost: Infinity Siege - Official Reveal Trailer (2023)
snippet.description:
Outpost: Infinity Siege will be released in 2023 Q3.

About the game:
Outpost: Infinity Siege is a first-person shooter that focuses on exploration, collection, base-building and survival elements, multiplayer online cooperation supported. 
Please note that the game is still in development and does not represent the final quality.

Follow us to enter the future Playtests:
